This version relates to CNS R78.
Remove SUNOS support and mention of SunOS or Solaris from makefiles.
Use $(CC) in place of gcc in a few places in makefiles.
Use LCLHOME for HOME in makefiles.
bbdcinit.c and bbdsinit:  Fix rare case where lnm was used uninitialized.
   Remove sunosbbdcquite as synonym for bbdcquit, used in place
   of atexit under SunOS.
